      "text": "Wiꞥſch dsers no tahß ly-\npes us Zetku/ tadeht pa-augsti-\nnahß wiꞥſch to Galwu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta CXI. Dseefma.\nIrr weena Pateikſchanas Dseefma teem Judu\nLaudim preeſcharakſita us Leeldeenũ dsee-\ndaht/ un Decwam pateikt/ ka tas ſawu Der-\nribu ar teem darrijs/ un ar wiſadahm\nLabdarrifchanahm pee Meeſas un Dwehfeles\nfwehti: I. xc\nAlleluja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "S pateizn tam KUN-\nGAM no wiſtas\nSirđs/ eekſch tahm\nRunnahm to Rahmu/ un eekſch\ntahs Drandſes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta KUNGA Darbi irr\nleeli/ tee tohp mekleti no wiſſeem/\nkam pee teem labs Prahts ir-\nraid.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Winna Darbs irr augsts\nun gehdigs/ un winna Taijmi-\nba pastahw muhſchigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch irr ſaweem Brih-\nnumeem weenu Peeminneſchanu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch dohd Barribu\nteem/ kas winnu bihſtahß/ un\nfawn Derribu peeminn tas muh-\nschaim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch leeß ſaweem Lau-\ndim ſawus ſpehzigus Darbus\nſtabſtihß/ ka wiꞥſch teem dohd to\nPagaxu Eemantofchann.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Winna Rohku Darbi irr\nPateefiba un Teeta/ wiſſi wiſ-\nna Bautli irr peetizzigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee tohp ſtiprinati muh-\nschigi muhſcham/ un noteek pa-\nteeſi un taijmi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch fuht Pestitchanu\nſaweem Laudim/ wiſch pawehß\nka winna Derribai buhs muh-\nschigi ſtahweht/ ſwehts un bih-\najams irr winna Wahrs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta KUNGA Bibjascha-\nna irr tahß Gudribas Gefah-\nkums/ teem irr labba Sapra-\nſcha...a/kaß to darra/ winna tei-\nzama Slawa pastahw muh-\nschigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta CXII. Dseefma.\nIrr weena Glawes Dseefma no teem Deewa-\nbihſtgeem/ka teem paſcheem no Deewa buhs\nſwehtiteem un eeprcezinatcem tapt wiſada\nNelaime: I. etc.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Alleluja: Swehtigs irr\ntas Wihrs/kaß to KUN-\nGU bihſtahß/ kam wiſ-\nna Bautli fohti patihß.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta paſcha Dſimmuns\nbuhs warrens wiſs Semmes/ to\nRahnu Zilts taps ſwehtita.\n"
    },
